{"title":"linux下编译安装stellar区块链","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.008Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/linux下编译安装stellar区块链","updated":"2023-07-28T09:12:01.721Z","content":"<h1 id=\"linux下编译安装stellar区块链\">linux下编译安装stellar区块链<a title=\"#linux下编译安装stellar区块链\" href=\"#linux下编译安装stellar区块链\"></a></h1>\n<p>stellar区块链有两种运行模式，一种是docker安装，一种是直接编译stellar-core的源码，进行安装</p>\n<ol>\n<li>首先是docker安装<br>\ndocker安装只需安装并启动docker</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install docker</span><br><span class=\"line\">service docker start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后执行代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run --rm -it -p &quot;8000:8000&quot; -v &quot;/home/scott/stellar:/opt/stellar&quot; --name stellar stellar/quickstart --testnet</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这就算启动了一个stellar-core+horizon的docker镜像</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>接下来主要是从源码编译并安装stellar-core<br>\n首先安装环境</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install git build-essential pkg-config autoconf automake libtool bison flex libpq-dev libunwind-dev parallel pandoc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>拉取stellar-core的源码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git clone https://hub.fastgit.org/stellar/stellar-core.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>cd stellar-core</code></li>\n<li>键入<code>./autogen.sh</code></li>\n<li>键入<code>./configure</code></li>\n<li>键入<code>make</code>（编译可能编译很久，耐心等待即可）</li>\n<li>键入<code>make check</code> (这步结尾可能会报fail的错误，无视即可)<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0c1c18f663ff4ca794fed253a4ff84c7.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/57cc4900ed8c4632b891923fe61a8c4a.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>键入<code>sudo make install</code><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/25bb6229ab9041d9820f0dca06af5cd9.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n安装完成后，在终端输入<code>stellar-core --help</code>会弹出提示，表示stellar-core安装成功<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/81a3c5daba8a4aaf9522ca487b547993.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n接下来安装数据库</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install postgresql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0239fd86bf97427a88d861f3c99377d0.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n配置数据库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo su - postgres</span><br><span class=\"line\">createuser -P stellar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/851cfda37e134abcb3e261a0e8f9868a.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n登陆数据库测试</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">createdb stellar</span><br><span class=\"line\">psql -U stellar -h 127.0.0.1 -d stellar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/415bbcf1e3c6409b93f6a27605118fec.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"operator\">/</span><span class=\"operator\">/</span>创建表</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"keyword\">table</span> test( id <span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"keyword\">primary</span> key, name <span class=\"type\">varchar</span>(<span class=\"number\">255</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">not</span> <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"operator\">/</span><span class=\"operator\">/</span>查看表</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\dt</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"operator\">/</span><span class=\"operator\">/</span>删除表</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">drop</span> <span class=\"keyword\">table</span> test;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"operator\">/</span><span class=\"operator\">/</span>退出</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\q</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/96e6a6f20eed43118a4626dcd8777e0d.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n配置数据库访问权限</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">//版本不同，路径上的数字也会不同</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo vi /etc/postgresql/<span class=\"number\">13</span>/main/postgresql.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0ce8cfed51ae41d6b9cc1fb625996f33.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n把<code>listen_address</code>的值修改成<code>*</code>,保存退出。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0702e0eee64a40f290497a32d2a13448.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n修改</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo vi /etc/postgresql/<span class=\"number\">13</span>/main/pg_hba.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/8cde9c34af9743e892a405f8084c3ad6.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n编写配置文件<code>stellar-core.cfg</code><br>\n参考git拉取的stellar-core/docs目录下的三个配置示例，根据你的环境配置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">stellar<span class=\"literal\">-core_example</span>.cfg</span><br><span class=\"line\">stellar<span class=\"literal\">-core_standalone</span>.cfg</span><br><span class=\"line\">stellar<span class=\"literal\">-core_testnet</span>.cfg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/de77e63e287248ca8f4c65e0fe54894a.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/672944a67f0041b2888a9033eaf69b55.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n参考示例配置，写完后，把你的<code>stellar-core.cfg</code>复制到<code>/usr/local/bin</code>目录下</p>\n<p>启动stellar-core</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#配置文件可以随便放，路径在--conf后面给出即可</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">stellar<span class=\"literal\">-core</span> <span class=\"built_in\">new-db</span> <span class=\"literal\">--conf</span> /usr/local/bin/stellar<span class=\"literal\">-core</span>.cfg</span><br><span class=\"line\">stellar<span class=\"literal\">-core</span> run <span class=\"literal\">--conf</span> /usr/local/bin/stellar<span class=\"literal\">-core</span>.cfg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c2b0bc1838a14351a77b83b9f114993a.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/3fef5dfa7482429eaa98c6b87b81c364.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>stellar-core启动完成后，在终端输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">curl</span> localhost:<span class=\"number\">11626</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>可以查看到stellar的页面信息。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/7626ed1f422a41d6ad67122c1cfd7006.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n此时即视为stellar-core编译和启动成功。安装完stellar-core之后可以参考<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/120240806?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501\" target=\"_blank\">这篇文章</a>，安装horizon组件<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/120240806?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/120240806?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"linux下编译和运行stellar区块链的horizon组件","link":"2023/07/28/linux下编译和运行stellar区块链的horizon组件"},"next":{"title":"linux下nginx的安装和配置","link":"2023/07/28/linux下nginx的安装和配置"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/linux下编译安装stellar区块链/","toc":[{"id":"linux下编译安装stellar区块链","title":"linux下编译安装stellar区块链","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"968 字约 6 分钟"}